data.description: A lovely Lewisville home located close enough to the amenities of WS but nestled in the tranquility of Lewisville living. A 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath, 1527 sq ft residence with 1 car attached garage and additional space for inside recreation. Includes spacious detached 2 car garage (24' x 24') great for vehicles, storage and/or workshopping.  This home has an ample backyard with deck and firepit - great for outside entertaining. The paved driveway can accommodate multiple vehicles and sellers are providing an American Home Warranty for one year. Welcome home to Lewisville!
